Find a Location






















Residential Builder 

Residential builders of all sizes rely on Builders FirstSource as a valued partner for their projects. Whether you are a national, regional, custom, or local builder, we understand your needs and deliver value to you every step of the way. Our prefabricated structural components, including roof trusses, floor trusses, wall panels, stairs, interior and exterior doors, windows, synthetic trim boards and mouldings, and engineered lumber deliver quality and efficiency. These components, combined with our large selection of high-quality building materials, first-rate installation services, and knowledgeable and experienced team, make Builders FirstSource the first source for residential builders.



















