Builders FirstSource Inc versus Continental Building Products Inc Head to Head Compare
				Date Published:
					
						2017-04-7
					
This is a head to head compare of Builders FirstSource Inc (NASDAQ:BLDR)  and Continental Building Products Inc (NYSE:CBPX) . We will compare the two companies on revenue growth, earnings, revenue per employee, operating margins, free cash flow and valuation. The head to head compare assigns 100 points in total. 
				


				Before we dive into the analysis, we will look at the stock returns for each company over the last three months, six months and the last year. The stock returns do not impact the head to head compare scores which are focused on the fundamentals of each company, but ultimately stock returns are are still a critical piece to a full analysis and compare.





