↪ Universal Forest Products Inc generates $1.06 in revenue for every $1 of expense, very similar to Builders FirstSource Inc's $1.05.Revenue per Dollar of Expense↪ UFPI generates $0.01 in levered free cash flow for every $1 of revenue, 
